metadata.name: REJECT FEAR
metadata.description:
Mixed Media on A2 Paper (420 x 594 mm);
Consisting of Oil Pastelle, Pencil, Fine liner pens, Paint, Coloured Pencils, Paper layering and Exacto knife.

I feel the appropriate title is 'REJECT FEAR' due to this piece allowing me as someone who is primarily a digital artist to venture into the traditional world. It was a lot of fun making this but still using my style and workflow from digital. It has opened my eyes to a new world for my work, and hopefully many more

Thank you and enjoy the physical!
